We can embed videos from both youtube and vimeo into your blog posts by using a shortcode.&nbsp;

`{% include youtubeplayer.html id=VIDEO-ID %}`

Insert that code into your blogpost where you want the video player to appear, then add the VIDEO-ID of the video you want to share.&nbsp;
